{
  "texts": [
    "We conducted 50 experiment runs for each item.",
    "We conducted two sets of statistical analyses to address two research questions.",
    "The first pertains to the degree to which ChatGPT demonstrates grammatical intuition comparable to that of human participants who are not necessarily linguists.",
    "To address this question, we integrated data sourced from ChatGPT with the human data.",
    "Following Sprouse et al. (2013), ratings were standardized by participants using z-score transformation."
  ]
}